{"tid":198952,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（敗走美國）MC Jin返美國專心湊仔","createTime":"2017-04-12T23:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T00:42:46.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e794f325bbd8a129b798cb6245d134b76feab4c","tid":198952,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"在邁阿密出生、父母為香港移民的MC Jin，2002年在黑人電視台（Black Entertainment Television）音樂節目上「Rap贏」黑人而聲名大噪，由美國紅回亞洲，先後在香港及台灣推出中文唱片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其後他轉戰大銀幕，簽約「大台」TVB後慢慢被家庭觀眾認識，更贏得2011年「飛躍進步男藝員」大獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，「囝囝」歐陽健（Chance）2012年在紐約出世後，<span style=\"color: red;\">MC Jin選擇急流勇退，低調地離開香港，回流美國繼續音樂創作。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"816aceb9b8afd42f8782936591d413a8db01d646","tid":198952,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢既美帝生活一定好過你班港豬囉"},{"pid":"035a995e9e61d8865bb40647de5f75c335994d7c","tid":198952,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:42:46.000Z","msg":"應該是敗走香港"}]}